    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>D3AD HAND now includes R3D STAR</strong> — a full new bonus and more challenging adventure featuring hours of new content!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Crack the code, feed the cat, save the world.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140810/extras/91b2df2e76cb222e82f8cb56246a947f.gif?t=1763590831\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140810/extras/91b2df2e76cb222e82f8cb56246a947f.poster.avif?t=1763590831\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>D3AD HAND</strong> is a darkly comedic point-and-click adventure set in a crumbling Cold War missile base deep in Siberia. You are <i>Yuri Spraytyvich</i>, freshly appointed Junior Strategic Missile Force Manager, tasked with holding together the decaying Čerëmuški Command Post.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But when <i>PERIMETER</i>—the Soviet automatic defense system—mistakenly initiates a nuclear launch, it’s up to Yuri (and your wits) to stop the end of the world. Navigate sabotage, radiation, worker strikes, and absurd bureaucracy in a race against doomsday. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140810/extras/fd2e674121dbdf79633bb7abd2c0d303.poster.avif?t=1763590831\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140810/extras/fd2e674121dbdf79633bb7abd2c0d303.webm?t=1763590831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>R3D STAR: </strong>Uncover the fate of Sputnik and thwart the devious plans of <i>Major Perestrova</i> in your continued quest to prevent global annihilation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◉ Unique alternative history setting and pixelart style. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◉ Tongue-in-cheek Humour.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◉ Elegant point 'n' click control of character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◉ Ideal for newcomers to the genre, familiar and nostalgic for veterans.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◉ Different endings to discover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◉ Play as Stalin in R3D STAR to help Yuri using your feline skills!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
